libg15render
------------------------------------------
This is a library to render text and shapes into a buffer usable by the
Logitech G15 Gaming Keyboard.

Runtime requirements:
  cygwin-2.9.0-2
  libfreetype6-2.6.5-1
  libg15render-devel-1.2-1bl3
  libg15render1-1.2-1bl3
  pkg-config-0.29.1-1

Build requirements:
(besides corresponding -devel packages)
  autoconf-13-1
  automake-9-1
  binutils-2.28-3
  cygport-0.24.1-1
  gcc-core-6.4.0-1
  libtool-2.4.6-4
  make-4.2.1-2

Canonical website:
  https://sf.net/projects/g15tools/

Canonical download:
  mirror://sourceforge/g15tools/libg15render-1.2.tar.bz2

-------------------------------------------

Build instructions:
  1. unpack libg15render-1.2-X-src.tar.xz
  2. if you use setup to install this src package,
     it will be unpacked under /usr/src automatically
        % cd /usr/src
        % cygport ./libg15render-1.2-X.cygport all

This will create:
  /usr/src/libg15render-1.2-X-src.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libg15render-1.2-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libg15render1-1.2-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libg15render-devel-1.2-X.tar.xz

-------------------------------------------

Files included in the binary package:

(libg15render)
  /usr/share/doc/Cygwin/libg15render.README
  /usr/share/doc/libg15render/AUTHORS
  /usr/share/doc/libg15render/COPYING
  /usr/share/doc/libg15render/ChangeLog
  /usr/share/doc/libg15render/NEWS
  /usr/share/doc/libg15render/README

(libg15render1)
  /usr/bin/cygg15render-1.dll

(libg15render-devel)
  /usr/include/libg15render.h
  /usr/lib/libg15render.dll.a
  /usr/lib/pkgconfig/libg15render.pc
  /usr/share/man/man3/libg15render.3.gz

------------------

Port Notes:

----- version 1.2-1bl3 -----
Rebuild with gcc-6.4.0

----- version 1.2-1bl2 -----
Rebuild on x86_64

----- version 1.2-1bl1 -----
